    "anticipation_contract": "Medium Swing anticipation remains region-first: the previous ChordRegion tail slot is computed from region duration, so 4-beat regions use local 4&/3.5, 2-beat regions use local 2&/1.5, and short regions are never forced through a bar-first 4& assumption.",
